{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">After death, your soul has entered the purgatory of eternal wandering. There is only one way out \u2014 to destroy the archdemon guarding the gates to freedom. Fight through hordes of restless souls, terrifying monsters, and demons. Collect the souls of fallen foes and use them to change your appearance. Play as anyone you destroy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1843650/extras/PH_GIF_1.gif?t=1736911608\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Soul Devourer</strong><br>Destroy and absorb the souls of your enemies and then play as them. A unique system that allows you to play as characters you have defeated. A vast number of characters with various classes and abilities, each with their own strengths and weaknesses, as well as their own development paths.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Development Path</strong><br>Level up your character. Each level can either grant or take away certain attributes. Enhance your character with artifacts and star stones.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Classes</strong><br>The game features a multitude of different classes. Each class has its own advantages that you can develop.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Star Map</strong><br>Collect star stones to improve the attributes of certain classes with the stargazer.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Artifacts</strong><br>Gather numerous artifacts scattered throughout purgatory. Some may enhance you, while others may harm you, sometimes all at once \u2014 the choice is yours.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Bosses</strong><br>Battle deadly bosses. You can even absorb the souls of some of them.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Dangerous Levels</strong><br>Purgatory is divided into many levels, and not all of them are harmless. Some levels impose weather, magical, and other effects on the player and other beings. Only the most resilient will survive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1843650/extras/PH_STEAM_GIF_2.gif?t=1736911608\" /></p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1843650/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736911608","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1843650/page.bg.jpg?t=1736911608","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1843650/51d62347eea8fe600746acb224e1f1af5c950d59/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1736911608","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1843650/51d62347eea8fe600746acb224e1f1af5c950d59/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1736911608","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">After death, your soul has entered the purgatory of eternal wandering. There is only one way out \u2014 to destroy the archdemon guarding the gates to freedom. Fight through hordes of restless souls, terrifying monsters, and demons. Collect the souls of fallen foes and use them to change your appearance. Play as anyone you destroy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1843650/extras/PH_GIF_1.gif?t=1736911608\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Soul Devourer</strong><br>Destroy and absorb the s